{"tid":134193,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（法律JJ) 咁樣可唔可以告佢刑毀 ?","createTime":"2017-02-25T09:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T14:29:55.000Z","uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"515c44207cd356113f7f39fced55b4c5a770418c","tid":134193,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"事源之前有人因為打爆左人地架車<br />\n之後要賠錢比人就問我借左幾千<br />\n但條友走我數<br />\n<br />\n佢自己WhatsApp record到表示係自己飲大左而打落人地架車到<br />\n內容有提及大約損壞部份 有地點<br />\n但實際日期同當事人就唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以報警 第三方咁舉報 ？<br />\n以我所知就係除非簽左和解協議<br />\n如果無就 責任都係佢身上<br />\n<br />\n成日見大家話留返同個官講<br />\n我以家純粹係好低機率收返錢既情況下<br />\n同時希望懲戒下條仆街 <br />\n唔知入唔入得罪 ？"},{"pid":"37225e16ddba994e17ae5c14317a8cdfb4185969","tid":134193,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n聽聞呢個只係藉口黎借錢還波馬數<br />\n所以我深信咩和解並不存在"},{"pid":"1a835e59cbad129178f17ab6249a8de554b9cbc9","tid":134193,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76885c663fbe523f8d8dfb025813be8be02f828","tid":134193,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e47ef23cc747b0306e5d871db463e5424aaa957e","tid":134193,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你成功</blockquote><br />\n個個都學您個名就仆街"},{"pid":"7c11e86e46a28ebe01963598a4c138fcfdd32e55","tid":134193,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763b005745840552dc7ef58ec16802ad1c437dc8","tid":134193,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm